    {
      "avalancheActivity": {
        "comment": "Na h\u0159ebenech Krkono\u0161 je 50 -80 cm sn\u011bhu. Nad 1300 m n. m. napadlo za 24 h 8 cm nov\u00e9ho vlhk\u00e9ho - mokr\u00e9ho sn\u011bhu v kombinaci s JZ v\u011btrem, pod 1300 m n. m. byly sr\u00e1\u017eky de\u0161\u0165ov\u00e9. Sn\u011bhov\u00e1 pokr\u00fdvka je vlhk\u00e1  v ni\u017e\u0161\u00edch poloh\u00e1ch hor a\u017e podm\u00e1\u010den\u00e1. \r\nB\u011bhem dne budou sr\u00e1\u017eky sn\u011bhov\u00e9 v kombinaci s Z a\u017e JZ v\u011btrem , pod 1300 m n. m. budou sr\u00e1\u017eky de\u0161\u0165ov\u00e9. \r\nV poloh\u00e1ch nad 1300 m n. m. se mohou vyskytnout laviny z nav\u00e1t\u00e9ho sn\u011bhu (S, SV, V, JV) nebo kombinace nav\u00e1t\u00e9ho sn\u011bhu a mokr\u00e9ho sn\u011bhu.\r\nPod 1400 m n. m. se mohou vyskytmout laviny z mokr\u00e9ho sm\u011bzu (v\u0161echny expozice).\r\nUvoln\u011bn\u00ed laviny je mo\u017en\u00e9 jen p\u0159i velk\u00e9m dodate\u010dn\u00e9m zat\u00ed\u017een\u00ed a to jen ojedin\u011ble ve velmi strm\u00e9m extr\u00e9mn\u00edm ter\u00e9nu. Je mo\u017enost samovoln\u00e9ho uvoln\u011bn\u00ed mal\u00fdch, nebo st\u0159edn\u00edch lavin, kter\u00e9 se v\u011bt\u0161inou zastav\u00ed je\u0161t\u011b na svahu.\r\n\r\nTendence lavinov\u00e9ho nebezpe\u010d\u00ed je setrval\u00e1."
